### Step 1: Create Cursor Watch Builder utilities (canonical location)

**File**: `src/cursor/watch-builder.ts` (new file)

All Cursor subagent utility functions live here (single source of truth):

```typescript
// Canonical location for subagentsDir derivation
export function getCursorSubagentsDir(sessionPath: string): string {
  return path.join(path.dirname(sessionPath), 'subagents');
