### 4. **Key Differences: Claude vs Codex Interactive**

| Aspect | Claude | Codex |
|--------|--------|-------|
| **Parser** | **Stateful**, one per session | **Stateless**, shared instance |
| **Handler Update** | N/A (createOnLineHandler uses parser map) | Via `let detectionHandler` closure |
| **Custom Title** | Yes (`onTitleUpdate` callback) | No (no rename command) |
| **Subagent Detection** | Event-driven (spawn/resume/toolUseResult) | Directory watch only |
| **Detector Type** | `SubagentDetector` | `CodexSubagentDetector` |
| **Session Handler** | `InteractiveSessionHandler` wraps SM+DC | Callbacks only (no session handler) |
| **File Scanning** | `scanForNewSubagents` (directory) | `extractCodexSubagentIds` (JSONL parsing) |

